title: What I Eat in a Day (Lately), Vegan in Kunming, China.
description:
Next is a $35 e-book: The Macrovore Diet.  Eat six bagels a day, do 200 push-ups, and get great results, or else I denounce you on the internet as a "fake vegan" who is secretly eating hamburgers, or working as a shill for the milk industry, etc.  Shout out to "my competition" at the microvore diet, BTW: we should, like, totally have a lawsuit together some time.*

* [If you don't know satire when you see it, I can't do nothing for you, man.]

In this case, I'm going to leave it up to the comments section to identify the vocalist/rapper.   ;-)
